&trans  &kp AR_ARABIC_KASRATAN  &kp AR_ARABIC_FATHATAN  &kp AR_ARABIC_DAMMATAN  &kp AR_ARABIC_SHADDA  &trans  &trans                                      &trans  &trans  &trans  &trans               &trans      &kp AR_ARABIC_SEMICOLON      &trans
